## 8. Storage

Active Storage is configured for two services:

- **local** — disk-based, used in development.
- **cloudflare** — Cloudflare R2 (S3-compatible) via the `aws-sdk-s3` gem. R2 quirks
  handled in `config/storage.yml`: `force_path_style: true`,
  `request_checksum_calculation: when_required`, `response_checksum_validation: when_required`.

Cover images on claims are auto-promoted from the first attached image among the
evidence files (see `Claim#promote_cover_image_from_evidence`), so members don't have
to upload a separate hero image.

The shared partial [`shared/_attachment.html.erb`](../app/views/shared/_attachment.html.erb)
renders any attachment with the right treatment: images and `mp4/webm/ogg` videos play
inline (with a download button overlay); other types render as a clean file card.
[`shared/_attachment_grid.html.erb`](../app/views/shared/_attachment_grid.html.erb) splits
visual vs. file attachments and lays them out together.

