## 9. Frontend

- **Tailwind CSS 4** with a custom Ghana-inspired palette (charcoal primary, gold
  accent, green success, red danger). Defined in
  [`app/assets/tailwind/application.css`](../app/assets/tailwind/application.css).
- **Stimulus** for sprinkles of interactivity — accordions
  (`evidence_accordion_controller`), file upload previews (`file_picker_controller`,
  `image_skeleton_controller`), the verdict picker, the multi-step claim form
  (`members_claim_form_controller`), etc.
- **Material Symbols** outline font for icons; SVG inline for special cases (chevrons,
  paper clips).
- **Plus Jakarta Sans** as the display font (no serifs, intentional choice).

Page-level layout conventions:

- Marketplace and inner pages: max-w-7xl for list pages, max-w-6xl for detail pages.
- Section headers on portal/detail pages: left-aligned title, right-aligned meta;
  homepage sections are centered.
- "Back" links: omitted on editorial pages (marketplace), included on portal detail
  pages.

